data.description: ONE OF THE BEST VALUES IN VAIL! NEW INTERIOR PAINT COMING NOV. 13, 2023. Enter this beautiful, open concept home; built for gatherings, entertaining or just a day to relax in comfort. The large loft is perfect for a home theater, game room or anything your imagination can dream up. Your entertaining can expand to the large backyard with real grass. The lot backs up to a common area for a more open feel. Gather around the fire pit on a cool desert night. . Do not miss the chance to view this incredible home that is move-in ready.
